body: @DanielaSchacherer Use something like Dependency Walker to see which component is not correctly configured on the file `[AnacondaRoot]\Lib\site-packages\torch\_C.cp36-win_amd64.pyd`. You can take this [answer](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/36778066/importerror-dll-load-failed-when-importing-numpy-installed-in-conda-virtual-env/42434616#42434616) as a reference.
